name: Claim Settlement Report
query:
select distributer as "Company:Link/Company:200",
 item as "Item:Link/Item:300",
sum(item_qty) as "Item Qty::100", 
free_item as "Free Item:Link/Item:300", 
sum(free_item_qty)as "Free Item Qty`::100" 
from 
   `tabScheme Management Log` 
group by 
    distributer, item, free_item
